quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  37,52,"Yambolelanga mbu: 'Toto ewe oli mubafuchililanga?"
  37,53,"Mbu nikhufwa, khwaba liloba nende ebikumba, mbu toto khulirungwa?'”"
  37,54,"Aliboola mbu: “Koo, enywe mulenganga (mumulilo)?”"
  37,55,"Kho alihenga ne alimulola hakari wa Jahannam."
  37,56,"Aliboola mbu: “Wallahi (nditsuba khu Nyasaye mulala)! Wali ahambi muno okhungosia."
  37,57,"Chikhayanga okhuba emikabo chia Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ndakhabeele mubalia abenjisibwamwo."
  37,58,"Koo! Efwe shikhulifwa tawe?"
  37,59,"Halali okhufwa khwefu khwokhuranga, nafu shikhulinyoola eshinyasio tawe.""
  37,60,"Toto khuno nikho okhubura okhukhongo."
  37,61,"Ne shinga kano, nikabakhole balia bakhola."
  37,62,"Koo, okhubukanilwa endi shinokhulayi, nohomba omusaala kwa Zaquum?"
  37,63,"Toto efwe khwakukhola okhuba eshinyasio khubalia abamabii."
  37,64,"Toto oko ni omusaala kurulanga hakari wa Jahannamu."
  37,65,"Ebibuli bia ebiamo biakwo bili shinga emirwe chia mashetani."
  37,66,"Toto abo balilia ebiamo ebo mana betsusie khubio tsinda tsiabu."
  37,67,"Mana khu ako bahelesibwe amaatsi kayile karabachila."
  37,68,"Mana obwatoto amakalushilo kabu kaliba Jahannam."
  37,69,"Toto bo banyoola basabwe nibakora."
  37,70,"Nabo nibakhola lwangu okhuloonda amaseenelo kabu."
  37,71,"Ne khubwatoto bamala okhukora imbeli wabu abandu bakhale abaanji."
  37,72,"Ne toto efwe khwabarumila abekanyilisi."
  37,73,"Mana henga olole shingala yali indukho yabalia abekanyilisibwa."
  37,74,"Halali Abasumba ba Nyasaye abalobole."
  37,75,"Ne toto Nuhu yakhulaanga, ne efwe khuli abalayi po bokhufuchilila."
  37,76,"Ne nikhumuhabina ye halala nende Abandu be okhurulana nende amasila amakhongo."